title: Ep. - 294 - DANCING WITH THE STARS, MTV CRIBS, AND POPSTARS
description:
Kate discusses two great shows from the early 2000’s, MTV Cribs and Popstars, which was the precursor to American Idol.

 

Host and actor Greg Zarian helps Kate review this season of Dancing with the Stars on ABC.
